        <a href="#research" class="hover:text-white">Research</a>
        <a href="#publications" class="hover:text-white">Publications</a>
        <a href="#teaching" class="hover:text-white">Teaching</a>
        <a href="#talks" class="hover:text-white">Talks</a>
        <a href="#skills" class="hover:text-white">Skills</a>
        <a href="#updates" class="hover:text-white">Updates</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO: text pushed far down so it sits BELOW the 3D shape -->
  <section class="relative z-10 mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 px-6 pt-[34rem] pb-24 md:grid-cols-[0.9fr_1.1fr] md:items-start md:pt-[26rem]">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_20%_70%,rgba(59,130,246,0.18),transparent_30%),radial-gradient(circle_at_80%_80%,rgba(168,85,247,0.18),transparent_30%)]"></div>

    <div class="flex justify-center md:sticky md:top-32">
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="absolute -inset-4 rounded-full bg-blue-500/20 blur-2xl"></div>
        <img
          src="/images/profile.jpg"
          alt="Masoud Ataei"
          class="relative h-72 w-72 rounded-full border border-white/20 object-cover shadow-2xl md:h-96 md:w-96"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <p class="mb-5 text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-blue-300">
        Machine Learning &middot; Mathematical Statistics &middot; Operations Research &middot; Time Series Analysis
      </p>

      <h1 class="mb-6 text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight md:text-7xl">
        Masoud Ataei, PhD
      </h1>

      <div class="mb-8 max-w-2xl space-y-4 text-xl leading-8 text-gray-300">
        <p>Hi! I'm Masoud.</p>

        <p>
          I am an Assistant Professor of Statistics in the Department of Mathematical and Computational Sciences at the <a href="https://www.utm.utoronto.ca/" target="_blank" class="text-blue-300 underline-offset-4 hover:text-blue-100 hover:underline">University of Toronto Mississauga</a>. I hold a Ph.D. in Mathematics and Statistics from <a href="https://www.yorku.ca/" target="_blank" class="text-blue-300 underline-offset-4 hover:text-blue-100 hover:underline">York University</a>, where my dissertation was unanimously nominated for the best dissertation prize.
        </p>

        <p>
          My research interests lie in <span class="text-gray-100">mathematical statistics</span>, <span class="text-gray-100">stochastic processes and nonstationary time-series analysis</span>, <span class="text-gray-100">tensor algebra, decomposition and low-rank learning</span>, and <span class="text-gray-100">mixed-integer, semidefinite and conic programming for interpretable artificial intelligence</span>.
        </p>

        <p>
          I am the inventor of several novel methods, including <a href="https://www.mdpi.com/1099-4300/28/2/157" target="_blank" class="text-blue-300 underline-offset-4 hover:text-blue-100 hover:underline">Lehmer Neural Networks</a>, the <a href="https://rdcu.be/cNsFa" target="_blank" class="text-blue-300 underline-offset-4 hover:text-blue-100 hover:underline">Lehmer Transform</a> for non-stationary signal representation, <a href="https://doi.org/10.3390/e26110996" target="_blank" class="text-blue-300 underline-offset-4 hover:text-blue-100 hover:underline">Derangetropy</a> for modeling information dynamics, and the <a href="https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0378437121004337" target="_blank" class="text-blue-300 underline-offset-4 hover:text-blue-100 hover:underline">Financial Chaos Index</a> for quantifying turbulence in financial markets. Previously, I served as the lead machine learning scientist on a <a href="https://www.yorku.ca/research/category/news/2019/05/researchers-win-1-89m-grant-to-search-for-ai-solution-to-infant-pain-assessment/" target="_blank" class="text-blue-300 underline-offset-4 hover:text-blue-100 hover:underline">$1.89M multi-institutional research program</a> on AI solutions for infant pain assessment.
        </p>

        <p>
          I always welcome opportunities for research collaboration and enjoy working with motivated peers.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-6">

        <a href="https://mcs.utm.utoronto.ca/~ataeimas/" target="_blank" class="transition hover:scale-110" title="Academic Homepage">
          <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
